      "type": "text",
      "title": "The Logotype",
      "text": "The logo and all graphic elements are based on one question: how do we show SaaStock’s main value – connection? We created a special symbol called the \"Link.\" By connecting two unique parts, this shape became the main graphic element and the foundation of the brand.",
      "variant": "dark",
      "padding": "compact"
    },
    {
      "type": "padded-media",
      "files": ["../../assets/projects/saastock/5.jpg"]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "A Clean but Vibrant Look",
      "text": "The challenge was to create a black-and-white brand that respects their history but also feels energetic. This is how we chose the color palette. When combined with the \"Link\" symbol, we can create many different shapes and frames to show the connections SaaStock helps build.",
      "variant": "dark",
      "padding": "compact"
    },
